node.title: Murder investigation begins after man's body found
node.description: The 19-year-old's body was found with a single gunshot wound.
node.content:
["", "
Conor O'Brien
", "Garda\u00ed (Irish police) have launched a murder investigation after a man's body was discovered in County Meath with a gunshot wound. ", "Conor O'Brien, 19, was found dead in the driveway of a house on Trim Road, Enfield on Friday morning, RT\u00c9 reports.", "Detectives said they believed the killing happened sometime after 20:00 local time on Thursday. ", "They have yet to establish a motive for the shooting.", "The victim, originally from County Wexford, had moved to the area four months ago and was due to start a job in the coming weeks. ", "", "
crime scene
", "He was living in an apartment at the back of a house on Trim Road.", "Detectives said Mr O'Brien was in contact with a family member around the same time he was killed. ", "No firearm was found at the scene.", "They said a number of people nearby heard a single bang on Thursday evening but it was not reported at the time. "]
